<body>
  <header></header>
  <main class="start-team-page">
    <div class="container start-team-shell">
      <a href="/start-team" class="btn btn-secondary back-button">&larr; Back to Steps</a>
      <p class="step-label">Step 2 of 6</p>
      <h1>Connect with FIRST</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Register your team with FIRST, find your region, and understand the official FTC process.</p>
      <section class="content-section">
        <ul>
          <li>Visit the <a href="https://www.firstinspires.org/team-registration" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">FIRST registration guide</a> for registration.</li>
          <li>Register your new team with FIRST and request a team number.</li>
          <li>Pay the annual FTC registration fee (usually around $500–600).</li>
          <li>Join your local FTC league and connect with regional events.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <div class="step-actions">
        <a href="/start-team-step1" class="btn btn-primary">Next: Choose a Sponsor Organization &rarr;</a>
      </div>
